title: Selva Kumar back in Malaysia
text:
More 
Convicted serial rapist Selva Kumar Subbiah arrived in Malaysia at about 7.30am this morning from Canada where he served a 24-year sentence for sex crimes and other related offences. 
Free Malaysia Today quoted a source close to Selva's family who said the 56-year-old, escorted by three Canadian police officers, had landed at Kuala Lumpur International Airport this morning and was greeted by his brother. 
"He (Selva) will remain in Kuala Lumpur and not return to Penang as initially expected," the source was quoted as saying.
